type: Tutorial Step - My Only Friend, The End!

definition.text: Ok, my friend, this is the end! I hope you've enjoyed the show and that I've managed to get you hooked to Superalgos!

paragraphs.text: There's no doubt in my mind that you haven't seen anything like Superalgos before. As you may now figure, Superalgos is a vast system and keeps growing fast.
There are many more ways in which you can help the project grow stronger!
That's it! No more steps after this one! I promise! Click Next if you don't believe me!
